# API Health Monitor - Project Rules

## Project Description
API Health Monitor is a lightweight Python CLI tool for monitoring API availability, performance, and health checks. It's designed for developers, DevOps engineers, and QA specialists who need fast API health checks without deploying heavy monitoring systems.

## Repository
https://github.com/maksim4351/api-health-monitor

## Key Features
- HTTP status and latency monitoring
- Configurable timeouts
- Multiple output formats (table, JSON, CSV, HTML)
- Web dashboard for real-time monitoring
- Email and Push notifications
- Result caching for performance
- Async support for parallel checks
- OpenAPI/Swagger documentation
- CI/CD integration with exit codes
- YAML configuration
- Zero dependencies on heavy monitoring infrastructure

